OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStaying dry and mostly cloudy,
OL,6,Fbut some bright spells with the cloud
OL,7,Fexpected to break at times. Feeling
OL,8,Fcool and fresh at times with light to
OL,9,Fmoderate north or northwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe evening will stay dry and
OL,12,Fmainly cloudy with the odd bright
OL,13,Fspell. Overnight again mostly dry but
OL,14,Fperhaps a light shower later.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FA cloudy start, perhaps a
OL,17,Flight shower or two over Orkney, then
OL,18,Fbrightening up from the north with
OL,19,Fsome sunny spells developing in the
OL,20,Fafternoon. Fresh northerly winds,
OL,21,Ffeeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
